<text top="1445" left="211" width="646" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t21" reading_order_no="20" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">to  earn  an  additional  $7  billion  once  the </text>
<text top="1492" left="210" width="401" height="49" font="font5" id="p1_t22" reading_order_no="21" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">plane  entered  production. </text>
<text top="1540" left="256" width="601" height="46" font="font7" id="p1_t23" reading_order_no="22" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">Almost  immediately,  things  started </text>
