<text top="1676" left="210" width="646" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t26" reading_order_no="25" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">revealed  that  their  aircraft,  based  on  an </text>
<text top="1722" left="210" width="649" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t27" reading_order_no="26" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">Embraer  commercial  jet,  was  rated  for </text>
<text top="1768" left="211" width="648" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t28" reading_order_no="27" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">only  9gs  of force,  not  the  16  that  the  Army </text>
<text top="1814" left="208" width="649" height="47" font="font3" id="p1_t29" reading_order_no="28" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">wanted.  Fixing  the  problem  drove  up  the </text>
<text top="1860" left="211" width="645" height="49" font="font5" id="p1_t30" reading_order_no="29" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">plane’s  weight,  putting  it  1400  kilograms </text>
